    "Moreover, the CXRs of all the retrospective datasets, including the CXR-AL14 dataset, held-out, and multicentre test datasets were de-identified to remove any patientrelated information before collection.",
    "None of the authors participated in the data de-identification process.",
    "The prospective test dataset was collected prospectively in accordance with procedures approved by the hospital Ethics Committee (no.",
    "2023-123-01) and written informed consent was obtained from each participant.",
    "The CXRs of prospective test datasets were also de-identified before transfer to study investigators."
